thread.title: BRIEF-Beibu Gulf Tourism sees FY 2017 net profit up 50 pct to 65 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Beibu Gulf Tourism sees FY 2017 net profit up 50 pct to 65 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - beibu gulf tourism corp ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Beibu Gulf Tourism Corp Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to increase by 50 percent to 65 percent, or to increase by 85 million yuan to 110 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 170.1 million yuan
* The main reason for the forecast is contribution from reorganization and acquisition Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/jSTRGd Further company coverage: (Beijing Headline News)
